                            <msPart xml:id="p6">
                                <msIdentifier/>
                                <msContents>
                                    <summary>Painting of the '<ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin Mary</ref>'</summary>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p6_i1">
                                        <locus target="#6v"/>
                                        <title>Description of the painting 'Virgin Mary'</title>
                                        <note>The text following the picture contains the title of the seventh miracle of the Virgin Mary (possibly, according 
                                            the counting of E. A. Budge: <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3593Miracle"/>). The owner, 
                                            <persName ref="PRS15036ZamanfasQ">Zamanfas Qeddus</persName> is mentioned as well: 
                                            <foreign xml:lang="gez">፯፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ በክልኤ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ ወምሕረተ፡ ፍቁር፡
                                            ወልዳ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብራ፡ ዘመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለዓለ<sic>ም</sic>፡ ዓለም።</foreign>. It is not clear, whether this text was indeed
                                            included in the description on the verso page of the painting, as it is assumed here, or is possibly copied as a caption 
                                            to the painting on the front page (cf. <ref target="#d6"/>).</note>
                                    </msItem>
                                </msContents>
                                <physDesc>
                                    <objectDesc form="Leaf">
                                        <supportDesc>
                                            <support>
                                                <material key="paper"/>
                                            </support>
                                            <extent>
